dcterms:description: A widely used dataset for handwritten digit classification, consisting of 70,000 images of handwritten digits from 0 to 9.

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of Zalando's article images, intended as a drop-in replacement for the MNIST dataset, containing 70,000 grayscale images of clothing items.
dcterms:title: Fashion-MNIST
